::DarkMouse/KitKat::

DarkMouse::
"Ok commander," as he snapped at her."I don't know who that is.  I 
see KitKat, but whoever the other bot is, KitKat appears to beleading 
them here."


KitKat::
Seeing the base in eye shot, she opened her link.
"Hey, I have Phobia here and he is joining us.  He wants to join in 
under Megatron.  Snd there is a bonus! He's got a really awesome 
gun.  It looks super powerful.  We'll be at the base in a few 
minutes."

She made herself to sound proud and had an inflating ego.  She hoped 
that this bot bought it all.
